<%= intro my_name: 'Helen', avatar: 'helen.png' do %>
  <p>Hi Kathryn, I’ve had a go at finding some things for you to do near WF1. I’m interested to see what you think of my suggestions. If I’ve got something wrong or you want me to find something else then let me know. I hope these ideas help you get more out of your area.</p>
<% end %>

<%= recommendation id: 'hepworth-gallery', why: 'You said you’d like to visit new places' do %>
    <h1><span>Have you been to The Hepworth in Wakefield?</span> According to Stephen Deuchar “It’s the museum everyone would dream of having on their doorstep.”</h1>
  <section class="recommendation-details">
    <header>
      <img src="<%= image_path 'hepworth.png' %>" alt="">
      <dl>
        <dt>The Hepworth Wakefield</dt>
        <dd class="availability">Open: 10am - 5pm every day</dd>
        <dd>Free entry</dd>
      </dl>
    </header>
    <div class="location-details">
      <%= map(latitude: 53.6760087, longitude: -1.4934895) %>
      <dl>
        <dd>Gallery Walk, Wakefield WF1 5AW</dd>
        <dd>27 minutes by bus <a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/dir//The+Hepworth+Wakefield,+Gallery+Walk,+Wakefield+WF1+5AW/@53.6759883,-1.5613401,12z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m9!4m8!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x48796657b3fd3437:0x26241f5938bf1cd7!2m2!1d-1.4913008!2d53.6760087!3e3" target="_blank">Get directions</a></dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="call-to-action">
    <div class="action">
      <h2>See what’s on</h2>
      <a href="https://hepworthwakefield.org/whats-on/" target="_blank">hepworthwakefield.org/whats-on/</a>
    </div>
  </section>
<% end %>

<%= recommendation id: 'walk-a-neighbours-dog', why: 'You said you’d like to walk a neighbour’s dog' do %>
  <h1><span>Do you want to find a neighbour’s dog to walk?</span> Borrow My Doggy is a website where people with dogs get matched with people who can help walk them!</h1>
  <p class="expanded-intro">You’ll have to register on their website to see what’s available and to start getting matched with a dog. You can do this for free with basic membership and upgrade if you find dogs that you want to walk</p>
  <section class="recommendation-details">
    <header>
      <dl>
        <dt>Borrow my doggy</dt>
        <dd>£12.99 per year for full membership</dd>
      </dl>
    </header>
  </section>
  <section class="call-to-action">
    <div class="action">
      <h2>Register on</h2>
      <a href="https://www.borrowmydoggy.com/" target="_blank">Borrow My Doggy</a>
    </div>
  </section>
<% end %>

<%= recommendation id: 'grow-garden-appltree', why: 'You said you’d like to grow a garden' do %>
